<paragraph id="8B8A3687FFC3F433F286490FFADDF7B7" blockId="0.[146,1430,1905,1960]" pageId="0" pageNumber="10">This new species is characterized by its large green saxicolous rosettes, a very thick curved peduncle bearing a more or less horizontal bright red cylindrical twice-branched inflorescence of about 20 short spreading branches.</paragraph>
